  "texts": [
    "Instead, imagine that recommender systems reliably directed our attention to the right things and in the right degrees.",
    "Would the moral skill of judicious attention allocation necessarily be well served?",
    "Would relying on automated systems, and not our own reasons-responsiveness, realize the same moral value?",
    "We don't think so.",
    "Attending to something only because it's been served up to you isn't as good as doing so for your own moral reasons."
  ],
